{"tid":2116122,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府鋪緊條靚路，準備誘導大家交出DNA資產，推行社會信用系統","createTime":"2020-07-20T03:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T14:07:45.000Z","uid":284416,"like":45,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f28599eb69e672177f24d0a987c0a6b64b8574","tid":2116122,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"成個地球都封晒除左中國無封你都有病毒，無情情零確診都會變返有。<br />\n又軟性宵禁又強制戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n目的顯而易見，就係要先推到盡影響你生活，店鋪生意。<br />\n迫你接受退一步既受監控自由，即係有健康碼先俾你出街食飯<br />\n<br />\n到時大家就好似朝三暮四既馬騮咁，以為皇恩大卸，自願交出自由，甚至仲會幫政府監察推行。<br />\n<br />\n健康碼就係一個包裝過既社會信用系統，中央系統可以以限制你生活自由既方式，間接令你變成一個順民。"},{"pid":"9f63d542541afd59cf100c6b134d9a6c92272226","tid":2116122,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"支那監控全面上場"},{"pid":"29e3b24404191122054be2ad7e79bb82162a4741","tid":2116122,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a36bf077c280c152f094c52140b43bec8ca0d91e","tid":2116122,"uid":11703,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"一早講咗防疫是假<br />\n仲要根本唔係啲咩可怕嘅病毒<br />\n<br />\n全香港有一個人一早講咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e42fec092179dc7902a3794a5410e1391bf574","tid":2116122,"uid":59461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"佢睇落似想搞宵禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5f0d8de8ff448df5bfcf8e8359eea82f0a1602","tid":2116122,"uid":232509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9987acf91aae29e7ffd1a306d6a4427d2f9e65f0","tid":2116122,"uid":92650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a36bf077c280c152f094c52140b43bec8ca0d91e","tid":2116122,"uid":11703,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"一早講咗防疫是假<br />\n仲要根本唔係啲咩可怕嘅病毒<br />\n<